          "segments": [
            "1. [1/81] al-Kafi: Muhammad b. Ismail from al-Fadhl b. Shadhan from Ibn Abi Umayr from Hisham b. al-Hakam and other than him from Abi Abdillah (as) who said: the Prophet (sw) addressed the people in Mina and said: O people, whatever comes to you attributed to me which agrees with the Book of Allāh then I have indeed said it, and whatever comes to you opposing the book of Allāh then I never said it."
